        "comment": "It's a great app but recently started giving problems when saving a photo edited using the native editor on the SD card storage. It had been working well (5 stars) until about a month ago. It is unacceptable for a cataloging/gallery app to not be able to manage/use permissions well. As for now, every time this happens, the fix is to uninstall/disable the app or revert the app to factory settings, and then start again. Simply resetting/denying-and-granting permissions doesn't help.",
